<emphasis box="[315,515,1523,1547]" italics="true" pageId="63" pageNumber="64">Adiscus pubiventris</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Medvedev, L. N." box="[521,694,1523,1547]" pageId="63" pageNumber="64" pagination="193 - 205" refId="ref43741" refString="Medvedev, L. N. (2008) To the knowledge of the genus Adiscus Gistel, 1857 (Coleoptera: Chrysomelidae: Cryptocephalinae). Russian Entomological Journal, 17, 193 - 205." type="journal article" year="2008">Medvedev, 2008</bibRefCitation>
