: A. habitus; B. lateral view of habitus; C. spermatheca; D. lateral view of aedeagus; E. dorsal view of aedeagus; F. ventral view of aedeagus; G. rectal pad. (Scale bars: A–B = 1.0 mm, C–G = 0.2 mm).
</paragraph>
